1
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:56,120
Help!

2
00:01:08,039 --> 00:01:09,000
It's you,

3
00:01:09,320 --> 00:01:10,720
Yan Qingshu.

4
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:13,039
Why did you ask me to meet in this remote place

5
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:14,640
and use such despicable methods

6
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,720
to assassinate me?

7
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:17,080
I

8
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,600
asked you to meet?

9
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,160
Yes.

10
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,460
And wanted to kill you?

11
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,280
Princess,

12
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,940
think about it carefully.

13
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:25,560
If I wanted to kill you,

14
00:01:25,840 --> 00:01:27,360
wouldn't it have been easier for that man in black

15
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:29,000
to just kill you directly?

16
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:30,520
I even came to save you

17
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:31,720
and stand before you.

18
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:36,860
This jade pendant.

19
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,200
Such a treasure,

20
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,920
how can you covet it?

21
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,320
Such a precious pendant,

22
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:47,440
the Princess should keep it safe.

23
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:50,840
Brother Jingyan,

24
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,880
come save me!

25
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:54,240
Yan Qingshu,

26
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,880
she wants to kill me!

27
00:01:56,479 --> 00:01:58,240
First, she sent someone in your name

28
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,720
to trick me into coming here.

29
00:01:59,720 --> 00:02:00,280
Then,

30
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:03,280
she used dirty tricks to assassinate me.

31
00:02:03,440 --> 00:02:05,280
She even choked me just now.

32
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:07,080
I almost lost my life!

33
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,280
Yes, I did it.

34
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,560
Brother Jingyan.

35
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,800
I wanted to kill her just now,

36
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,120
choked her and tore her clothes.

37
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:13,880
It wasn't enough to vent my anger,

38
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,920
so I hung her on a tree and whipped her dozens of times,

39
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:18,050
yet let her stand here perfectly fine.

40
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,760
Princess, your wound,

41
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,680
if you don't treat it soon,

42
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:26,540
I'm afraid you'll bleed to death.

43
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,920
You... you...

44
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:55,320
Miss Yan, you've been staring at me all the way.

45
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,720
Why don't you come closer

46
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,160
to see more clearly?

47
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,640
The jade pendant on Cui Linlang's neck,

48
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,840
did you give it to her?

49
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,720
Sort of.

50
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,080
A token of love?

51
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,730
You could say so.

52
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,360
It seems

53
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,760
your relationship with Prince Ling's Mansion

54
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:24,960
is very close.

55
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,120
I'm very curious.

56
00:03:28,640 --> 00:03:29,880
What poison is on

57
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,410
Miss Yan's silver needles?

58
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,160
Jianfenghou.

59
00:03:33,320 --> 00:03:34,200
Want to try?

60
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,090
I'm just saying.

61
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:40,440
I did have a marriage agreement with the Cui family.

62
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:42,400
But it was arranged by the Empress Dowager,

63
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,860
and I canceled it long ago.

64
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,880
As for that jade pendant,

65
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,570
she made a fake one herself.

66
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:51,460
Does the grand Princess of Prince Ling's Estate

67
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:54,120
need a fake to keep up appearances?

68
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:56,940
There's something you don't know, Miss Yan.

69
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,380
This Black Dragon Pendant

70
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:01,210
is a treasure of my Xiao family,

71
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,170
passed down through generations.

72
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:06,500
Only the wife of the Xiao family heir can have it.

73
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:08,440
I think

74
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,520
you are jealous, Miss Yan.

75
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:15,200
What nonsense are you talking about?

76
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,260
I'm talking about serious business.

77
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:18,399
That day,

78
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,680
why did you deliberately let Xie Yuheng go?

79
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:23,600
Letting him escape from prison is the real dead end for him.

80
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:26,120
It ruins the century-old reputation of the Xie family,

81
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,840
making them despised by everyone.

82
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,240
And it makes Xie Yuheng

83
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,360
like a stray dog,

84
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:34,280
eventually executed in constant panic.

85
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:39,020
Isn't this more satisfying than just killing him with one strike?

86
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,920
Can't you

87
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,880
trust me a little more?

88
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:57,890
What did this person do?

89
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,080
Read it to us.

90
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:08,570
Execute without mercy.

91
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,820
Still execute without mercy.

92
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,730
I have found out.

93
00:05:17,840 --> 00:05:20,640
The Second Miss of the Yan family disguised herself and sneaked into the prison,

94
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:22,040
and took Xie Yuheng away.

95
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,090
If Xiao Jingyan didn't let them go,

96
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,780
could they escape unscathed?

97
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,960
You are wise, Your Highness.

98
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:35,600
Xiao Jingyan is deliberately releasing the tiger back to the mountain

99
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:37,520
to ruin the Xie family's reputation

100
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,960
and destroy their good name.

101
00:05:38,960 --> 00:05:40,560
It is a devastating psychological blow.

102
00:05:40,560 --> 00:05:42,420
This move is extremely ruthless.

103
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,000
Where is the son of the Xie family?

104
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:46,400
I have sent men to secretly search the city.

105
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,480
Xie Yuheng is too ashamed to return home,

106
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:50,120
so he must be hiding somewhere.

107
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:53,580
It's only a matter of time before his whereabouts are exposed.

108
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,420
No need to look.

109
00:05:58,840 --> 00:05:59,770
He is not stupid.

110
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,620
Since he knows I want his life,

111
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,160
the only place he can hide

112
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,760
is there.

113
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,560
Please see the truth, Empress Dowager.

114
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:17,040
The Beidi envoy was indeed killed by Prince Ling,

115
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,240
and he framed me.

116
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,320
I am completely powerless.

117
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,920
I only know how to wield a pen.

118
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,920
How would I dare lift a sword to kill?

119
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:29,280
Xiao Jingyan let you out like a dog.

120
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,560
Didn't he just want to use your mouth

121
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,400
to bring Prince Ling's dirty deeds

122
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:35,080
before me?

123
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:38,659
Every batch of weapons Lord Ling sent to the Northern Frontier

124
00:06:40,640 --> 00:06:43,680
is stamped with the Empress Dowager's phoenix seal.

125
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,840
Lord Xie,

126
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:52,640
are you trying to frame the Empress Dowager for colluding with Lord Ling

127
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:54,200
and committing treason?

128
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:57,490
I am willing to swear on the lives of my entire Xie family.

129
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,440
If I speak a single lie,

130
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,480
may I die without a burial place.

131
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:07,520
Lord Ling is trying to drag me down

132
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,080
to be buried with him.

133
00:07:09,800 --> 00:07:10,800
Empress Dowager.

134
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,800
Forging the phoenix seal and secretly colluding with the Northern Di

135
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,640
is punishable by the execution of nine generations.

136
00:07:14,640 --> 00:07:17,840
Lord Ling is truly insane.

137
00:07:18,400 --> 00:07:19,840
I originally thought

138
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:22,520
Lord Ling was your right-hand man,

139
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,240
so I showed him some respect.

140
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:25,820
Who would have thought

141
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,760
he never respected you,

142
00:07:28,320 --> 00:07:29,840
and harbored rebellious intentions all along.

143
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:30,600
Enough.

144
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,040
I have my own judgment.

145
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:39,320
Since you are here, Minister Xie,

146
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,600
take a look for me.

147
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:44,080
In Prince Ling's furnace,

148
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,480
are they forging blades for Beidi,

149
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,400
or coffin nails for me?

150
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,280
I

151
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,920
accept Your Majesty's decree.

152
00:08:19,280 --> 00:08:20,120
Aunt Qin.

153
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:23,560
We really are connected.

154
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,800
I was just thinking of you,

155
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,680
and here you are.

156
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,560
Aunt Qin.

157
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,080
I missed you.

158
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,660
Many things have happened recently.

159
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,559
I wanted to talk to you.

160
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,640
The usual.

161
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,440
Spleen deficiency, stomach cold,

162
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,570
blocked meridians,

163
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:48,400
restlessness,

164
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,520
and poor sleep.

165
00:08:50,440 --> 00:08:51,600
How could you

166
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:53,170
ruin your health like this?

167
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,080
Quick, follow me to the Lingzhi Pool

168
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:56,410
and soak for four hours.

169
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,040
Aunt Qin.

170
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:08,860
The water is ready.

171
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,260
Don't look at me like that.

172
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:37,920
If you want to blame someone, blame Yan Qingshu.

173
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:41,090
Only by killing the people she cares about

174
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,000
will her heart

175
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:46,080
break into pieces.

176
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,800
Carving out her heart

177
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:51,720
will relieve my hatred.

178
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:52,880
Let

179
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,240
Qingshu go.

180
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,720
Let her go.

181
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,480
Will she let me go then?

182
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:00,800
Please.

183
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,600
I beg you.

184
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,000
Aunt Qin.

185
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:57,840
Aunt Qin.

186
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,080
Aunt Qin.

187
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,560
Aunt Qin.

188
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:36,120
Qingshu.

189
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:42,800
Madam Qin.

190
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:57,840
Aunt Qin, can you teach me how to make elixirs?

191
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,770
There are no elixirs in this world.

192
00:12:00,160 --> 00:12:02,760
However, I can teach you to prepare

193
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:04,640
a few emergency antidote prescriptions.

194
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:06,720
They can save your life in a crisis.

195
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,200
Do you want to learn?

196
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:10,600
Will it save my parents' lives?

197
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:12,560
I'll learn.

198
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,060
Aunt Qin, Aunt Qin.

199
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,060
Smell this.

200
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:25,920
This is the new antidote I made.

201
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:28,120
It cures both snake and scorpion venom.

202
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,600
Aunt Qin.

203
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,880
I've pretty much mastered

204
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:35,620
the study of detoxification.

205
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,840
When will you teach me how to make poisons?

206
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:40,280
You've been living in the valley for half a year.

207
00:12:40,280 --> 00:12:43,480
It's time to write to the Yan Mansion to send someone to take you back.

208
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,160
I'm not going back.

209
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:47,520
If I go back, who will talk to you and make medicine with you?

210
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,880
Besides, if I leave,

211
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,320
won't you miss me too?

212
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,240
Right?

213
00:12:51,280 --> 00:12:52,360
I'm not leaving.

214
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,400
Fine, I'll teach you.

215
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:56,160
Aunt Qin.

216
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:59,060
I also want to learn acupuncture.

217
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:01,210
And flying needles.

218
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,480
Aunt Qin.

219
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:32,120
I, Yan Qingshu, swear here,

220
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:36,740
I will definitely avenge you.

221
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,200
Rest in peace.

222
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:03,970
Qingshu.

223
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,360
Cuimei.

224
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:31,960
Cuimei.

225
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:33,600
Yong.

226
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:35,640
Huachao.

227
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:35,640
Kun.

228
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:36,640
Weikun, Huachao.

229
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:39,840
Long, Cong, Biao, Hao.

230
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:43,680
Shuang, Bin.

231
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:44,160
Shuang.

232
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:45,160
Ningzheng.

233
00:14:47,160 --> 00:14:48,760
Hao, Chun, Kang, Shuai, Hua.

234
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:53,000
Weichao,

235
00:14:53,000 --> 00:14:53,600
Wei, Chao.

236
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:56,170
Qiang, Yuan, Liang, Bo.

237
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:13,760
Xi.

238
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,720
Tao, Qiang.

239
00:15:18,320 --> 00:15:19,800
Hui, Yue, Yun, Qing.

240
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,200
Yiyi.

241
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:28,960
Si, Si, Si.
